OL,3,CPope Francis cancels meeting with Rome
OL,4,Cdeacons due to illness
OL,6,FPope Francis has cancelled an audience
OL,7,Fscheduled for Saturday as a precaution
OL,8,Fafter coming down with mild flu, the
OL,9,FVatican press office said in a short
OL,10,Fstatement, without adding further
OL,11,Fdetails.
OL,13,FFrancis was scheduled to meet with
OL,14,FRome deacons in the morning.
OL,16,FVatican spokesman Matteo Bruni said
OL,17,Flater on Saturday that the pope's
OL,18,Fweekly Sunday Angelus address was
OL,19,Fstill to be confirmed, and that no
OL,20,Ffurther health updates were expected
OL,21,Ffor the day.
