OL,3,CPope Francis cancels meeting with Rome
OL,4,Cdeacons due to illness
OL,6,FThe 87-year-old pontiff has had
OL,7,Fseveral health problems in recent
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FIn late November, he was forced to
OL,11,Fcancel some of his activities and an
OL,12,Finternational trip because of
OL,13,Fbreathing problems. A scan at the time
OL,14,Fruled out lung complications.
OL,16,FFrancis had a part of one lung removed
OL,17,Fwhen he was young and still living in
OL,18,Fhis native Argentina.
