OL,3,CPope Francis cancels meeting with Rome
OL,4,Cdeacons due to illness
OL,6,FIn April, the pope spent three days at
OL,7,FRome's Gemelli hospital for what the
OL,8,FVatican said was bronchitis. He was
OL,9,Fdischarged after receiving intravenous
OL,10,Fantibiotics.
OL,12,FFrancis also spent 10 days at the same
OL,13,Fhospital in July 2021 following
OL,14,Fintestinal surgery for narrowing of
OL,15,Fthe bowel.
OL,17,FHe was readmitted in June 2023 for an
OL,18,Foperation to repair an abdominal
OL,19,Fhernia and remove scarring from
OL,20,Fprevious surgeries.
